<td>5-15%</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Time to results</td>
<td>1-4 weeks</td>
<td>3-6 months</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Relationship required</td>
<td>Warm (they already linked)</td>
<td>Cold (new contact)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Cost per link</td>
<td>$0-50 (DIY)</td>
<td>$300-1,000 (agency)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
