<h2>Chapter 6: Best Practices for Maximum Success &#123;#ch6&#125;</h2>
<p>These practices separate successful reclamation campaigns from failed ones.</p>
<h3>Prioritize by Link Value</h3>
<p>Not all lost links are worth recovering. Focus your energy on links that will move the needle.</p>
<p><strong>Priority scoring system:</strong></p>
